OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FA man from Deganwy in Conwy says he
OL,8,Ffeared he may die after spending 44
OL,9,Fhours on a corridor at Ysbyty Glan
OL,10,FClwyd before having his gallbladder
OL,11,Fremoved, which had become gangrenous.
OL,13,FIt comes as new figures reveal almost
OL,14,F89,000 patients were treated in
OL,15,Fcorridors or other non-clinical
OL,16,Fenvironments between 2022 and the end
OL,17,Fof October 2025 in hospitals run by
OL,18,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,19,FBoard.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
