FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FIn February this year, an undercover
OL,8,Finvestigation by the S4C current
OL,9,Faffairs programme Y Byd ar Bedwar
OL,10,Ffilmed dozens of patients receiving
OL,11,Fcare on corridors in the emergency
OL,12,Fdepartments at two North Wales
OL,13,Fhospitals.
OL,15,FJournalists also spoke with 40 people
OL,16,Fwho said they had witnessed or
OL,17,Fexperienced corridor care in hospitals
OL,18,Frun by the health board. A nurse at
OL,19,FYsbyty Gwynedd, who spoke anonymously,
OL,20,Fclaimed treating patients in corridors
OL,21,Fhas become "normal".
OL,26,@}D@LOU}D@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
