CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,F'I thought I was going to die'
OL,9,FSteve Jones, 68, spent 44 hours on a
OL,10,Fcorridor at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd in
OL,11,FOctober 2025.
OL,13,FHe went to the hospital's emergency
OL,14,Fdepartment with severe stomach pains.
OL,15,FAfter being assessed by the triage
OL,16,Fteam, he was placed on a corridor.
OL,18,F"It was like a warzone," he said. "I
OL,19,Fthought I was going to die, to be
OL,20,Fhonest. It was frightening."
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FHis partner, Haf Poole, stayed with
OL,8,Fhim throughout the experience. A
OL,9,Fformer nurse who worked at Wrexham
OL,10,FMaelor Hospital until retiring in
OL,11,F2020, she said she was concerned he
OL,12,Fwas not receiving the care he needed.
OL,14,F"He wasn't safe on the corridor," she
OL,15,Fsaid. "There were no monitors, no drip
OL,16,Fstands, nothing really."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@aO]wD@GOUxD@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FAfter two days in hospital receiving
OL,8,Fantibiotics and fluids through a drip,
OL,9,FMr Jones said a doctor told him he
OL,10,Fcould go home. Ms Poole said she
OL,11,Fchallenged that decision because she
OL,12,Fbelieved he was too unwell to be
OL,13,Fdischarged.
OL,15,FAfter this, Mr Jones was sent for a
OL,16,Fscan, given a diagnosis and moved to a
OL,17,Fward bed overnight. On his third day
OL,18,Fin hospital he underwent surgery to
OL,19,Fremove his gallbladder, which had
OL,20,Fbecome gangrenous.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FMs Poole said the surgeon was
OL,8,Fsurprised by the condition of the
OL,9,Forgan.
OL,11,F"He said it was the worst gallbladder
OL,12,Fhe'd seen in years," she said.
OL,14,FShe believes her partner might not
OL,15,Fhave survived if he had been
OL,16,Fdischarged.
OL,18,FShe said: "If Steve had gone home, he
OL,19,Fwould have have sepsis, he would have
OL,20,Fdied."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@TO]zD@KOU|D@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FMr Jones said the experience had
OL,8,Fshaken his confidence in the health
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,F"It's definitely shaken me and I'd be
OL,12,Fscared of going back there," he said.
OL,14,FFigures show patients received
OL,15,Fcorridor care for almost 10 hours on
OL,16,Faverage at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd last
OL,17,Fyear, the longest average wait among
OL,18,Fhospitals in North Wales.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
