OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FHealth board response
OL,9,FIn a statement, Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,10,FUniversity Health Board said it
OL,11,Frecognised that too many patients were
OL,12,Fwaiting too long in emergency
OL,13,Fdepartments.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FIt said: "Like NHS organisations
OL,8,Facross the United Kingdom, we are
OL,9,Fexperiencing both significant demand
OL,10,Ffor urgent and emergency care and
OL,11,Fchallenges in the timely discharge of
OL,12,Finpatients from hospital. At times,
OL,13,Fthis means some patients wait longer
OL,14,Fto be seen, receive treatment and be
OL,15,Fadmitted.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, some patients are
OL,8,Fcared for in non-designated or
OL,9,Fcorridor spaces. We have put in
OL,10,Fadditional clinical oversight to help
OL,11,Fensure patient safety however we know
OL,12,Fthis can be a distressing experience
OL,13,Ffor patients, their families and our
OL,14,Fstaff. We are very sorry to anyone who
OL,15,Fhas experienced long waits or received
OL,16,Fcare in these circumstances."
OL,18,FThe statement continued, stating that
OL,19,Fthe health board is looking at
OL,20,Fimprovements it can make.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FIt read: "Improving patient experience
OL,8,Fin our Emergency Departments, and
OL,9,Fsupporting our staff to provide the
OL,10,Fbest care possible, is the top
OL,11,Fpriority for the Board. Working
OL,12,Fclosely with our local authority
OL,13,Fpartners, we are implementing a
OL,14,Fsignificant programme of improvement
OL,15,Facross the health and social care
OL,16,Fsystem to improve the flow of patients
OL,17,Fthrough our hospitals, include safe
OL,18,Fdischarge. We are also learning from
OL,19,Fbest practice with a team of external
OL,20,Fexperts working within the health
OL,21,Fboard bringing experience from across
OL,22,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,F"Despite challenging circumstances,
OL,8,Fstaff in our Emergency Departments and
OL,9,Fright across the Health Board provide
OL,10,Fexpert emergency care day in, day out,
OL,11,F24 hours a day. We know that the vast
OL,12,Fmajority of the public respect and
OL,13,Fsupport them to do this really
OL,14,Fimportant work."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government said: "We are
OL,8,Fclear that the delivery of care in
OL,9,Fundesignated or non-clinical
OL,10,Fenvironments is not acceptable. It
OL,11,Fcompromises patient dignity, safety,
OL,12,Fand staff wellbeing, and we are
OL,13,Fdetermined to end this practice
OL,14,Fthrough system-wide reform.
OL,26,@oD@\OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/21
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
