OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,F"We have placed an experienced
OL,8,Fintervention team into North Wales to
OL,9,Fsupport the health board to improve
OL,10,Fpatient experience and outcomes, as
OL,11,Fpart of the level 5 special measures
OL,12,Fprocess. We have also committed an
OL,13,Fadditional #200 million across Wales
OL,14,Fto better manage staffing, same day
OL,15,Femergency care, and community
OL,16,Fservices, with a further #2.7 million
OL,17,Fspecifically for Betsi Cadwaladr to
OL,18,Freduce pressure on emergency
OL,19,Fdepartments.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/21
