FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773745531
OL,3,C'Thought I was going to die':
OL,4,CInvestigation reveals reality of
OL,5,Ccorridor care
OL,7,F"We continue to discuss concerns
OL,8,Frelating to patient experience and
OL,9,Fpatient and workforce safety directly
OL,10,Fwith the health board's senior leaders
OL,11,Fand will continue to hold the health
OL,12,Fboard to account through established
OL,13,Foversight arrangements."
OL,15,FWatch Y Byd ar Bedwar: Gofal ar
